high_descs: Walk through an exit in the upper right, go right down the corridor, get in a room on the right and then to the opposite corner, in front of the coffeetable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Go back to the entrance of the room you were in the beginning, go straight to the side of a bed where a lemon is, and face the bed.
Cut the lemon on the bed with the knife.
Go back to the room you picked the knife from, and walk to the coffeetable.
Place the knife on the coffeetable.
Go back to the bed in another room where you cut the lemon.
Pick up the lemon from the bed.
Leave the room and go right all the way and this time enter the bathroom straight in front of you and and stop in front of a sink.
Place the lemon slice in the sink, rinse the lemon out and take it out.
Move back to the room with the coffeetable you put the knife on.
Put the lemon slice on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed-out Lemon on the CoffeeTable
